name: Folder Structure
description: Enforces a consistent frontend folder layout and TypeScript file placement.
tags: [structure, frontend, react, typescript]
---

- Place admin components in `src/admin/components`.
- Frontend React components in `src/frontend/components`.
- Shared components in `src/shared/components`.
- Shared utilities belong in `src/utils`.
- React hooks in `src/hooks`
- React stores for admin `src/admin/stores/`
- React stores for frontend `src/frontend/stores`
- React shared stores `src/shared/stores`
- Admin Views are stored in `src/admin/views`
- Frontend views as stored in `src/frontend/views`